title: Alfred Stieglitz - Photographs and Writings (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
pdf / english / 1999 / 246 pag / 18 MB

Alfred Stieglitz (1864-1946) was a pioneering photographer, a towering figure on the American arts scene, and the husband of Georgia O'Keeffe.

73 of Stieglitz' finest photographs spanning his entire carreer, including 56 letters and articles.This book accompanied the exhibition in the National Gallery of Art in Washington.
